==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Emmetropic
<hw>Em`me*trop"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Pertaining to,
or characterized by, emmetropia.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The normal or <qex>emmetropic</qex> eye adjusts itself perfectly
for all distances.</q> <rj><qau>J. Le Conte.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Emmetropy</ent>⟦br⟧
